Course Management System(like Canvas)

-Online Platform
        Data: Students, Professors, calender, mail box, student portal , teacher portal
        Behaviours:

-Student
        Data: UserID, email, program details
        Behaviour: login
                   check class schedule
                   join meetings
                   listen to recording
                   submit assignment
                   send email
                   start discussion

-Professor
        Data: UserID, email, list of courses
        Behaviour: login
                   start meetings
                   post assignments
                   start recording
                   grade students
                   send email
                   start discussion

-Calender
        Data: Dates, events
        Behaviours: give reminders
                    display events

Pseudo code:
OnlinePlatform canvas;
Student jessy;
Professor dan;

StudentPortal sp = jessy.login(jessy.userID, jessy.password);
TeacherPortal tp = dan.login(dan.userID, dan.password);
if(calender.givesClassReminder)
    dan.startMeeting;
    jessy.joinMeeting;
    dan.recordMeeting;
else
    jessy.checkClassSchedule;
if(jessy.missedMeeting)
    jessy.accessRecording;
if(jessy.hasADoubtFromClass)
    if(jessy.wantsToDiscussWithClass);
        jessy.postAnnouncement;
    elseIf(jesyy.wantsToAskTA);
        jessy.sendEmail(TA.emailID);
if(dan.postAssignment);
    jessy.submitAssignment;
    if(jessy.submitAssignment)
    dan.gradeJessy;











